# GPT-2 RA: Baseline vs Routing (1-hour each)
#
# Tests the RA inductive bias: route compute based on |x - E(x)|
# to use cheap attention for easy tokens, full attention for hard.
#
# Step 0: Baseline (all heads as FULL, no routing)
# Step 1: RA with routing (router decides compute tier)
#
# Both use same code path through RABlock for fair comparison.

